 +-----------------+       +------------------+
      |  ESP8266 (NodeMCU)      |  Sensors         |
      |                         |                  |
      | A0  <-------------------+ Anemometer (DCG) |
      | D4  <-------------------+ DHT11 (DATA)     |
      | D1(SCL), D2(SDA) <-----> BMP180 (I2C)      |
      |                         |                  |
      | Wi-Fi --> Blynk IoT     |                  |
      +-----------------+       +------------------+
